property.description: Welcome to 9304 Ravenswood Road, an exceptional RIVERFRONT RETREAT in prestigious PECAN PLANTATION COUNTRY CLUB, on the serene banks of the BRAZOS RIVER. This home offers a unique blend of luxury, tranquility and outdoor adventure, perfect for those seeking an UPSCALE LIFESTYLE with direct river access. Open concept layout with elegant finishes & large windows framing the breathtaking view. The kitchen is a chef's dream with granite counters, center island, breakfast bar & large walk in pantry. The spacious living area, with a cozy gas fireplace, flows effortlessly into the dining area and sunroom making it ideal for entertaining. The luxurious primary retreat features river views, a spa like shower, dual vanities, jetted tub & a large walk in closet.  Two additional bedrooms feature a jack & jill bath and walk in closets. Situated on 1.525 acres, there is endless space to play & entertain. Oversized garage with workbench & golf cart garage, new gutters, new deck, new sprinkler system, new firebox and freshly painted kitchen cabinets.  Washer, dryer and two refrigerators convey and most of the furnishings are negotiable. Residents enjoy exclusive amenities such as golf, tennis, swimming, equestrian facilities and commercial conveniences including a grocery store, bank, medical offices, veterinarian, coffee shop, bistros, Ace Hardware & more. This home combines country club living with the natural beauty of riverfront property, providing an unmatched lifestyle. Don't miss your opportunity to own this extraordinary home on the BRAZOS RIVER.

property.description: **$100k reduction! Use this to complete the remaining updates... This home has the potential to be a true showstopper! Nestled on a coveted three-acre riverfront lot in Pecan Plantation, this exceptional home offers privacy, space, and stunning views. Thoughtfully designed with high-end finishes throughout, it features new stone in the kitchen and bathrooms, adding both style and function.The main level boasts four bedrooms, including a spacious primary suite & a bonus space that could be used for a study, office or formal dining. The primary bathroom is a true retreat, featuring luxurious finishes and a spa-like atmosphere. A huge screened-in porch provides the perfect space for relaxing or entertaining while taking in serene river views.Upstairs, a versatile bonus space is currently used as a theater room and second primary but offers endless possibilities - it could serve as a game room, second living area, private apartment, or multi-generational suite. The giant bedroom and full bathroom, make it ideal for guests, tenants, or extended family. Be sure to see the private walk out balcony overlooking the lush property, perfect for morning coffee or stargazing in the evenings.  A rare opportunity to own one of the most sought-after properties in Pecan Plantation - don’t miss your chance to experience riverfront living at its finest! Beyond the home, Pecan Plantation offers an unmatched lifestyle with a country club, two golf courses, a private airstrip, two pools, pickleball and tennis courts, archery, trails, a dog park, a marina, shopping, restaurants, equestrian stables, an RV park, and more.More neighborhood information at ppoaweb.com
